Package: Power
Title: Power Calculations
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Zachary",
           family = "McCaw",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "zmccaw@alumni.harvard.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2006-9828"))
Description: Power and sample-size calculations for regression models.
    Supports linear regression (Y ~ X + Z) and logistic regression with
    centered covariates. Computes power for Wald tests of H0: beta_X = 0
    and finds sample size for a target power via numerical search.
